{"tid":1478860,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"教協反對罷課？？","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:36:56.000Z","uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6da7207b1cf388f002f7b97e55630f6ded9b64","tid":1478860,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"啱啱嚇一跳，睇TVB  摘錄講到教協反對罷課咁<br />\n睇返全文唔係咁講，但到lee 一刻都仲未決定。<br />\n咁多學生比人捉左，你地仲未支持罷課。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教協塵該要在８月最後一個星期宣布支持罷課。<br />\n<br />\n教協教育界議員葉建源說：「長期是這樣(罷課)，對香港社會、對學生發展，都是一個很大的問題，所以渴望政府能回應大家的訴求。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d56c510e60383864847534f/%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%93%AC%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8%E6%97%A5%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E6%95%99%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8A%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d56c510e60383864847534f%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25BF%2592%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0fZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=7a380375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d56c510e60383864847534f/%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%93%AC%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%96%8B%E5%AD%B8%E6%97%A5%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E6%95%99%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8A%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83</a>"},{"pid":"41608271b7aa485dd70006e4384b8257c078c4ba","tid":1478860,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}